    "assessments": [
        {
            "assessment_detail_section_id": "assessment-detail-0",
            "assessment_title": "Seminar Presentation",
            "special_indicators": [
                {
                    "special_indicators_class": "icon--standard--alert-triangle icon-text--small",
                    "special_indicator_text": "Hurdle"
                }
            ],
            "weighting": "<dd>40%</dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 19/08/2026 - 28/10/2026</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>Presentation dates will be allocated in Week 1.</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": null,
            "mode": "Activity/ Performance",
            "category": "Presentation",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>In small groups students will lead 40-60 minute group discussion based on an allocated weekly topic. Your presentation should not just summarise the topic, but should encourage the class to discuss larger issues/questions that arise from the topic. You are encouraged to draw on additional source material to supplement your presentation, if it would advance the discussion. </p>\n<p>The focus of this assessment is not just on your understanding of the topic but how effectively you are able to engage the group and facilitate collective learning and productive discussion during the session. Students may chose to incorporate class participation, group activities and question-and-answer style content.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>",
            "late_submission": "<p>A <a href=\"https://policies.uq.edu.au/document/view-current.php?id=184\">penalty</a> of 10% of the maximum possible mark will be deducted per 24 hours from time submission is due for up to 7 days. After 7 days, you will receive a mark of 0.</p>",
            "additional_info": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>"
        },
        {
            "assessment_detail_section_id": "assessment-detail-1",
            "assessment_title": "Essay",
            "special_indicators": [
                {
                    "special_indicators_class": "icon--standard--alert-triangle icon-text--small",
                    "special_indicator_text": "Hurdle"
                }
            ],
            "weighting": "<dd>40%</dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 23/10/2026 5:00 pm</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": null,
            "mode": "Written",
            "category": "Essay/ Critique",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>The goal of the essay is to showcase your understanding of a topic that is germane to the materials covered in the course. Your essay (1500-2000 words) does not need to focus on a paper or topic that has specifically been covered in the course. The scope of your essay and the specifics of what you would like to cover will need to be negotiated with the course coordinator. Your essay must not have significant overlap with your presentation topic. </p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>via Turnitin</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You may be able to <a href=\"https://my.uq.edu.au/information-and-services/manage-my-program/exams-and-assessment/applying-assessment-extension\">apply for an extension</a>.</p>",
            "late_submission": "<p>A <a href=\"https://policies.uq.edu.au/document/view-current.php?id=184\">penalty</a> of 10% of the maximum possible mark will be deducted per 24 hours from time submission is due for up to 7 days. After 7 days, you will receive a mark of 0.</p>",
            "additional_info": "<p>You may be able to <a href=\"https://my.uq.edu.au/information-and-services/manage-my-program/exams-and-assessment/applying-assessment-extension\">apply for an extension</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
            "assessment_detail_section_id": "assessment-detail-2",
            "assessment_title": "Active Seminar Participation",
            "special_indicators": [
                {
                    "special_indicators_class": "icon--standard--alert-triangle icon-text--small",
                    "special_indicator_text": "Hurdle"
                }
            ],
            "weighting": "<dd>10%</dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 17/08/2026 - 26/10/2026</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": null,
            "mode": "Oral",
            "category": "Participation/ Student contribution",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>Active participation in the seminar sessions is essential for the course. Just as presenters will be expected to lead group discussion, audience members will be expected to engage with the speakers and discuss the material being presented in a thoughtful and constructive manner. Your participation in each session will be assessed on a pass/fail basis based on the quality (not quantity) of your contribution.</p>\n<p><br/></p>\n<p>If you are unable to participate actively during the session for whatever reason, please discuss with me ahead of time. </p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>",
            "late_submission": null,
            "additional_info": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>"
        },
        {
            "assessment_detail_section_id": "assessment-detail-3",
            "assessment_title": "Topic Questions",
            "special_indicators": [],
            "weighting": "<dd>10%</dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 17/08/2026 - 28/10/2026</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>Questions must be submitted <strong>at least 24 hours prior to class</strong>. </p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": null,
            "mode": "Written",
            "category": "Participation/ Student contribution",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>For each presentation week (Weeks 4-13) students will submit 2-3 questions via BlackBoard regarding the topics covered that week. It is expected that student questions will be informed by each weeks topics/readings and can serve as jumping off points for class discussion.</p>\n<p>Students do not need to submit questions for the week in which they are presenting.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
